<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1007</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a nǐ shì wǒ bái rì de yún zhù, zhǔ a nǐ shì wǒ hēi yè de huǒ zhù.
 wǒ yī lù zǒu lái, nǐ dōu bǎo hù. nǐ shì wǒ yī shēng de guī sù.
 yǒu nǐ wǒ jiù yǒu yī qiè, méi yǒu nǐ yī qiè dōu méi yǒu. wǒ de xīn qīng qīng chǔ chǔ,
 zhǔ nǐ shì wǒ yǐn dǎo. zhǔ nǐ shì wǒ suǒ yǒu, nǐ shì wǒ yī shēng de yún zhù huǒ zhù.</lyrics>
<title>nǐ shì wǒ yī shēng de yún zhù huǒ zhù 迦南1007</title>
</song>